snippet.title: Best VGM 1909 - Dragon Ball Z : Super Butoden - Imperfect Cell's Theme
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 275 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lXBFPdRiZMs

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Dragon Ball Z : Super Butoden (1993)
Imperfect Cell's Theme
Kenji Yamamoto & Kumagorou
